{"title":"信息语丝","authors":["关国培"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":9,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"信息语丝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　信息灵，出金银。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　货畅其流，信息牵头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　庄稼人讲节令，生意人讲信息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　信息反馈快，生意通四海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　商品经营，信息先行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　信息灵，点子多，路子广。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　一条信息，一条富路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　掌握信息先人一步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　人才要精，信息要新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　靠信息指挥，上马心中有数；下马调头有路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△　人才是支柱，信息是生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关国培　辑"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}